# excirclesRadicalCircle

- _excirclesRadicalCircle(t)_

Answer the excircles radical circle of the triangle _t_.

~~~spl svg=A
let t = [4.5 3 5].sssTriangle;
[
	t,
	t.excirclesRadicalCircle,
	t.spiekerCenter.Point
].LineDrawing
~~~

